title: Turbo Tax Home and Business 2013
description:
Key Features of TurboTax Home & Business CD/Download:

Get help finding small-business tax deductions
We'll tell you which expenses you can deduct for your vehicle, supplies, utilities, home office expenses, and more, so you get every business tax deduction you deserve.
Tax deduction
Spot industry-specific tax deductions
We'll walk you through tax write-offs by industry to help you spot commonly overlooked deductions.
Maximum tax deductio
Get the biggest vehicle tax deduction
We'll tell you if actual expenses or the standard mileage rate will get you the biggest tax deduction. We can also give you extra help for splitting vehicle expenses between business and personal use.
Big life changes
Enter income easier
We'll show you all business income types on a single page so you know you've covered all sources of business income reported on Schedule K-1, Schedule Q and Schedule C.
Audit Risk Meter
Get help creating W-2 and 1099 tax forms
Prepare unlimited forms for employees and contractors and print them all on plain paper. No special forms needed. (Note: Mac users must have Internet access to create W-2 and 1099 tax forms.)
Education tax credits
Simplify asset depreciation
We can help you determine which depreciation method will get you the biggest tax deduction. Then we'll guide you through calculating and reporting depreciation.
features-placeholder
Streamline expense entry
We'll walk you through all expense categories. We also offer additional tax deduction suggestions along the way so you can maximize your savings.
Education tax credits
Extra guidance for new businesses
We'll show you the startup tax deductions new businesses can take.
